'''Pech''' ([[ungrikani ćhib|ungrikanes]]: ''Pécs'',[[romani chib|romanes]]: "Pechuj" vay "Pecho", [[kroatikanes]]: ''Pečuh'', [[jermanikanes]]/nyamcicka: ''Fünfkirchen'', [[serbikanes]]: ''Pečuj'' or ''Печуј'', [[slovaika]]: ''Päťkostolie'', [[latinikanes]]: ''Quinqueecclesien'', [[turkikanes]]: ''Peçuy'') si o shtarto baro [[foro]] la [[Ungariya]]ko, ko sudovesto le [[them]]esko. Si o [[xulyaripnasko mashkar]] la rigyako [[Baranya]]. Sas janglo pe jermanikanes sar ''Fünfkirchen''; ando [[Romayako thagaripen]] lesko anav sas ''Sopianæ''. O anav pe jermanikanes, latinikanes thai slovaika amboldel pes ''Panj khangerya''.

Pech sas alosardo te avel o [[Europikano foro le sanskrtipnasko]] ando bersh [[2010]].

